snippet.textDisplay: I'm italian and I've been following you for almost a year. I used to watch your videos to learn english and improve my listening, but a few time after, I started to watch them because you're funny, smart and a sunny person. I didn't even care about makeup (and I'm still not interested 😬), I just liked you and your presence. I can't understand how frustrating was to live in a body you don't feel you belong to, but I can understand how hard is to coming out in this world and especially if you're followed by millions of people, you've been so brave. So thank you so much for let me learn your language and for telling us your story, proudly and with that beautiful smile on your face. ✊🏳️‍🌈
